fsqtbuild_i18n_finalVersion.other: FINAL VERSION, NO MORE UPDATES EVEN IF REQUESTED, BUILD ENVIRONMENT HAS BEEN DESTRUCTED

fsqtbuild_i18n_sqlite.other: SQLite (distributed with Qt) are built in the package using `%s`

fsqtbuild_i18n_odbc_sqlite.other: ODBC and SQLite (distributed with Qt) are built in the package using `%s`

fsqtbuild_i18n_icu.other: All builds have `%s` because I think the ICU library is too big and, in most of the conditions, useless for common users.

fsqtbuild_i18n_emsdk.other:
All packages are built using emscripten SDK %s as recommended in Qt Wiki.  
WebAssembly doesn't support ABI compatibility. You MUST use SDK %s for building your own code, otherwise unpredicted error may occur.

fsqtbuild_i18n_emsdk_thread.other: All builds have thread feature enabled using `%s`.

fsqtbuild_i18n_wasm_static.other: Qt for WebAssembly can only be built to static libs.
